<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <title>Password reset request</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h3>
      Password Reset Request
    </h3>

    <p>Hi <b>{{name}}</b></p>

    <p>It looks like you need help with your password. We're on it.</p>
    <p>Please reset your password by clicking on

      <a href="{{link}}">
        Reset Password
      </a>
      <p>If didn't request for this, simply ignore. Nothing will change in your
        account settings, and your account will be secure</p>
    </p>

    <p>Be aware that this link is only valid for the next 15 minutes</p>
  </body>
</html>